Chopped Canada - Season 1, Episode 21




Pressed for Ham

The chefs are hard pressed to impress in this appetizer round featuring canned meat and kohlrabi. Three remaining chefs give us something to "root" for when they combine bacon and this Asian vegetable. Ultimately one chef will "beet" out a victory with a sweet and spicy dessert basket.




Original Air Date: 22-May-2014
